    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given medium model influence, corroborating analytical sensitivity analysis, and the fact that all three QoIs pass quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is judged sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
